    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Steel nails each having a deformed shank, often helically threaded, having a countersunk head and a short diamond-shaped point.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
